💡 Slide Title: What is Databricks?

Databricks is an all-in-one platform that unifies data and AI workloads in the cloud.


---

✅ Key Capabilities (Visual Icons Recommended)

🪣 Data Lake: Store all your raw and structured data at scale with Delta Lake

📊 Business Intelligence: Enable dashboards and reporting with powerful query performance

🏢 Data Warehouse: Use SQL for fast, reliable analytics — warehouse-grade performance

🧠 AI & Data Science: Build, train, and deploy ML/AI models with notebooks and MLflow

⚙️ ETL & Data Engineering: Automate pipelines with notebooks, workflows, and Delta Live Tables

📈 Real-Time Analytics: Stream, process, and analyze data as it arrives

📅 Orchestration: Schedule and manage multi-step workflows with built-in workflow engine



---

🔽 Optional Bottom Tagline:

> Built on open standards. Designed for scalability. Ready for enterprise AI.



